                    Project Architecture

                  +------------------+
                  |  Frontend (UI)   |
                  |  index.html      |
                  +--------+---------+
                           |
                           v
        +-----------------------------------------+
        |              MMT Service                |
        |         (Port: 8082, WebClient)         |
        +-------------------+---------------------+
                            |
                            | HTTP (GET)
                            v
        +-----------------------------------------+
        |              IRCTC Service              |
        |      (Port: 8081, PostgreSQL DB)        |
        +-------------------+---------------------+
                            |
                            | JPA (INSERT/SELECT)
                            v
                    +-------------------+
                    |   PostgreSQL      |
                    +-------------------+



